      "span_text": "While the concept of living successfully with aphasia is not a new one (Brown et al., 2012;  , an asset-based approach provides and strong theoretical basis and a practical framework (e.g. Hopkins and Ripon, 2015; Ripon and South, 2017) to enable this transformation."
